{
  "stem": "3928.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Leslie Banos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born in Nyirbator, Hungary, which spells N-Y-I-R-B-A-T-O-R, in August the 16th, 1923.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's the-- that's a small town located on the northeastern part of Hungary, approximately 20 miles of the Romanian border and 30 miles of the present Russian border.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My name was given to me, Laszlo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came to the United States, everybody had a hard time saying, Laszlo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then officially, I changed my name to Leslie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "L-A-S-Z-L-O, that's Laszlo.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Too many Hungarians have it, and I didn't want it to have it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she died when I was approximately 10 months old.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my relatives in Budapest took me, and they raised me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were what they call, Hungarian Evangelikus, which means, like Lutherans, you know, non-practicing Christians, so to speak, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they were social democrats as such.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was raised by them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were a kind of a people, you know, who believed in equality and-- and the socialist and the equalist system, you know, for people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was raised with the respect to all people, regardless race, wealth, or religion, and because my uncle, he was a head of the steelworkers' union.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was also the-- a senator for the Social Democratic Party in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was the editor of the socialist newspaper called, which means, the 'Voice of the People.' And in this milieu, I was raised.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, my other uncle, you know, his son had a factory called Vanczak Csobutorgyar, which means, Vanczak-- the name, V-A-N-C-Z-A-K.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the name of his name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he used that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He built like a steel manufacturing plant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He did everything, from hospital beds, to bicycles, and baby-buggies, everything in their factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
